      "raw": "{\"prompt\": \"Use case: illustration-art\\nAsset type: fine art print, vertical scroll\\nPrimary request: traditional Chinese ink wash landscape painting with mountains, mist, pine trees, thatched cottage, and an old fisherman by the stream\\nScene/backdrop: layered mountain ranges fading into distance, ethereal mist swirling between peaks, serene mountain stream in foreground\\nSubject: distant mountains like dark ink wash, pine trees with gnarled branches, rustic thatched-roof cottage, elderly scholar in traditional robes fishing by the stream\\nStyle/medium: traditional Chinese ink wash painting (shanshui), xieyi freehand brushwork, rice paper texture\\nComposition/framing: vertical scroll format, three-layer composition (foreground stream and figure, middle ground trees and cottage, background misty peaks), generous negative space\\nLighting/mood: soft diffused natural light through mist, tranquil and contemplative atmosphere, ethereal and timeless\\nColor palette: monochromatic ink tones (black, gray, white), subtle blue-green mineral accents on distant peaks, warm sepia on cottage\\nMaterials/textures: rice paper absorbency, dry brush texture for pine bark, wet ink bleeding for mist, calligraphic line work\\nConstraints: preserve traditional Chinese painting aesthetics, maintain intentional negative space (liu bai), emphasize spiritual emptiness and vastness\\nAvoid: photorealistic detail, bright saturated colors, western perspective, heavy outlines, cluttered composition\", \"size\": \"1024x1536\", \"quality\": \"medium\", \"n\": 1, \"output_format\": \"png\"}",
